<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a15Aug1925"><font color="red">15 August 1925</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Ernest Walsh): You have not replied to my letter from Niort &hellip; My sight is getting worse, I think, so I shall be very glad if you will have the piece set at once and sent to me. I will correct it and the other piece at the same time &hellip; It does not matter if your review is delayed a few days after 30 September as long as it is dated September &hellip; I am glad that you found the piece suitable. </div>
